title: CONUS - Current Large Fires in the US - Incidents 12-24 hours ago, USA, 10:00 am 10.26.2007
name: CONUS - Current Large Fires in the US - Incidents 12-24 hours ago, USA, 10:00 am 10.26.2007
description: This Dataset shows the locations of large Wildfires in the USA for a time range of 12-24 hours ago. Large wildfires are 100 acres or more occurring in timber, or  wildfires of 300 acres or more occurring in grass/sage.
